Palearctic winter visitor, mainly coast: all around coast N of equator and to S Tanzania in east; also Niger Delta, Nile Valley and Rift Valley to Tanzania.
Lakes, rivers, bogs, moors, grasslands, and coastal marshes; in winter, also seacoasts, estuaries, and bays.
